'''新加坡建国之父'''（{{lang-en|Founding fathers of Singapore}}）是指[[主权国家|现代国家]][[新加坡|新加坡]]的建国元勋，准确来说并不是由[[新加坡政府|新加坡政府]]授予的正式称号，而是指参与争取[[新加坡独立|新加坡独立]]的多名政治人物。<ref name=pm>{{cite news|title=PM Lee on Singapore's founding fathers|url=http://news.asiaone.com/News/AsiaOne+News/Singapore/Story/A1Story20100830-234725/2.html|publisher=AsiaOne News|date=2010-08-30|accessdate=2015-02-22|quote=Dr. Goh didn't make his contributions alone. He was part of a team of founding fathers who built our nation. Besides MM Lee and Dr. Goh, they included Mr. Rajaratnam, Dr. Othman Wok, Mr. Lim Kim San, Mr. Hon Sui Sen, Mr. E.W. Barker, Dr. Toh Chin Chye and others.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221214848/http://news.asiaone.com/News/AsiaOne+News/Singapore/Story/A1Story20100830-234725/2.html|archivedate=2015-02-21}}</ref>

被称为“新加坡建国之父”的人物包括（根据英语名字顺序排列）：
# [[蒂凡那|蒂凡那]]（C. V. Devan Nair），新加坡全国职工总会秘书长、第3任新加坡总统
# [[大卫·马绍尔|大卫·马绍尔]]（David S. Marshall），新加坡辩护律师、前新加坡首席部长
# {{tsl|en|Edmund W. Barker|埃德蒙·W·巴克}}（Edmund W. Barker），新加坡政治家<ref name=pm />
# [[吴庆瑞|吴庆瑞]]（Goh Keng Swee），首任新加坡财政部长、首任内政及国防部长<ref name=pm /><ref>{{cite web|author=Roy|title=Dr Goh Keng Swee, a Founding Father of Singapore|url=http://www.nlb.gov.sg/blogs/highbrowseonline/non-fiction/dr-goh-keng-swee-a-founding-father-of-singapore/|publisher=新加坡国家图书馆管理局|date=2007-07-27|accessdate=2015-02-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221214220/http://www.nlb.gov.sg/blogs/highbrowseonline/non-fiction/dr-goh-keng-swee-a-founding-father-of-singapore/|archivedate=2015-02-21}}</ref>
# {{tsl|en|Hon Sui Sen|韩瑞生}}（Hon Sui Sen），新加坡政治家、第4任新加坡财政部长<ref name=pm />
# [[李光耀|李光耀]]（Lee Kuan Yew），首任新加坡总理<ref name=pm /><ref>{{cite web|title=100 Leaders: Lee Kuan Yew|url=http://100leaders.org/lee-kuan-yew|publisher=National History Day|accessdate=2015-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221205638/http://100leaders.org/lee-kuan-yew|archive-date=2015-02-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
# [[林金山|林金山]]（Lim Kim San），新加坡政治家<ref name=pm />
# {{tsl|en|Ong Pang Boon|王邦文}}（Ong Pang Boon），新加坡政治家<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pmo.gov.sg/newsroom/mr-ong-pang-boon%E2%80%99s-eulogy-late-mr-lee-kuan-yew|title=Mr Ong Pang Boon’s Eulogy for the late Mr Lee Kuan Yew|quote=总的来说，他是一位有远见、有勇气去实现理想的领袖，没有他，就没有今天的新加坡。|access-date=2017-05-15|archive-date=2019-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115055303/https://www.pmo.gov.sg/newsroom/mr-ong-pang-boon%E2%80%99s-eulogy-late-mr-lee-kuan-yew|dead-url=no}}</ref>
# [[奥斯曼渥|奥斯曼渥]]（Othman Wok），新加坡政治家<ref name=pm />
# [[拉惹勒南|拉惹勒南]]（S. Rajaratnam），首任新加坡外交部长<ref name=pm /><ref>{{cite web|author=Averil|title=Mr. S. Rajaratnam – The Singapore Lion|url=http://www.nlb.gov.sg/blogs/highbrowseonline/general/mr-s-rajaratnam/|publisher=新加坡国家图书馆管理局|date=2010-02-03|accessdate=2015-02-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221212621/http://www.nlb.gov.sg/blogs/highbrowseonline/general/mr-s-rajaratnam/|archivedate=2015-02-21}}</ref>
# [[杜进才|杜进才]]（Toh Chin Chye），首任新加坡科学及工艺部长<ref name=pm /><ref>{{cite web|author=Wan Ni|title=Singapore’s Founding Father Toh Chin Chye Passes|url=http://www.nlb.gov.sg/blogs/highbrowseonline/obituaries/singapores-found-father-toh-chin-chye-passes/|publisher=新加坡国家图书馆管理局|date=2012-02-05|accessdate=2015-02-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221212616/http://www.nlb.gov.sg/blogs/highbrowseonline/obituaries/singapores-found-father-toh-chin-chye-passes/|archivedate=2015-02-21}}</ref>

